review: This was a lot of fun! We did the Gold Rush room - I want to go back!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Austin in Austin
review: It was awesome. I honestly went in thinking I wasn't going to like this game. We did the Gold Rush, didn't escape, but it was fun. Can't wait to go again!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Austin in Austin
review: A group of friends and I recently enjoyed escaping from The Gold Rush scenario at The Escape Game in Austin. We're all 30 something women and had a blast! Each room only takes an hour, but you do need to have as many people as the room calls for - it helps get through the puzzles faster.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Austin in Austin
review: Wow!!!!! Never experienced anything quite like this!!!!! Loved every minute of the challenge with my family & friends. The environment that was created was amazing down to every detail, including sound effects & smells. Everyone in our group was challenged & had an opportunity to make a contribution. Can't wait to return to Austin to take on another Escape Game challenge.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Austin in Austin
review: Amazing game! There's enough to do for everyone, no matter the size of the group. Arriving early helps you organize your group. The hint posted on the game page really helped us out! My friends absolutely loved it
